; Spindle-sync bracketing test (G33). Verifies SET_SPINDLESYNC is armed then
; cleared within the block, so no stale sync leaks to later moves / programs.
G21 G90 G94
M3 S500
G0 X0 Y0 Z2
G33 Z-5 K1.0        ; spindle-synchronized feed (pitch 1mm/rev)
G0 Z2
G1 X10 F600         ; plain feed AFTER G33 — must NOT be spindle-synced
M5
M2
